name: Jack the tripper
description: Jack the tripper, CircusMinds is a creational art project using the stixart.com colour code to create art, meaning all pieces of art are unique and all say something, either hidden or shown, the colour codes can be changed to any colours you like, for example from a famous picture, this means only the person with the code will ever know what each piece of art says so up to them if they keep it a secret or reveal all.
